    "en": {
      "title": "An announcement from the Maldives Speaker",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has resigned from his post, the speaker and former president of Maldives, Mohammad Nasheed, said in a tweet.",
        "He says that Sri Lanka can now move forward and that if the President was in Sri Lanka, he would not have resigned due to fear for his life.",
        "Mohammad Nasheed also says that he appreciates the thoughtful actions of the people of Maldives.",
        "My warm greetings to the people of Sri Lanka, according to his tweet."
      ],
